title: Grateful Dead Live at Knickerbocker Arena on 1993-03-28
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Walkin' Blues, So Many Roads, When I Paint My Masterpiece, High Time, Eternity, Deal

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Wave To The Wind-> Truckin'-> Drums-> Jam-> Way To Go Home, Attics Of My Life, Turn On Your Love Light, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door
